  "body": "## Proposal\r\n\r\nNot really a big problem, but nice if it is easy and fast to accomplish:\r\n\r\nToday, I analyzed and tried to fix problems with some scrapes. Therefore, to see all the problematic scrape-targets, I used the UI: Status -> Targets.\r\n\r\nThere, I clicked on `Unhealthy`, which showed the sections where the `State` is `DOWN`.\r\nWhen I refresh the page, it again shows `All`, and I have to click `Unhealthy` again, which is annoying when I have to refresh the page mutiple times.\r\n\r\nIt would be more user-friendly, I if the site would go to `Unhealthy` again after a page reload/refresh.\r\n\r\n* Prometheus version:\r\n\r\n\tv2.4.0 docker version",
